/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人呀，在丹麥既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁有啲是有外國護照既香港人既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}